Class WeaponsTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.model.WeaponsTest
  • public class WeaponsTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Tests about the correctness of weapon actions. User connection is emulated by always choosing the first available choice.
